message: >-
  Cite the archive as a dataset. When citing a specific text, also cite its
  original source, edition, provenance metadata, and applicable rights record.
type: dataset
title: Ilyenkov Philosophy Text Archive
authors:
  - name: Ilyenkov Philosophy Text Archive contributors
repository-code: https://github.com/hoshF/Ilyenkov-cn
