abstract: >-
  A source-traceable archive of original-language philosophical texts,
  bibliographic and provenance metadata, digitization infrastructure, and
  Chinese translation research centered on Evald Ilyenkov.
keywords:
  - Evald Ilyenkov
  - Soviet philosophy
  - philosophy text digitization
  - digital humanities
  - source criticism
